<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="by-prep">by <strong><em>prep</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /baɪ/    美 /baɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>在...旁；靠近：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Come and sit by me. 
过来坐在我身旁。</p></div>

<h3 id="by-near">辨析 by, near</h3>
<p>二者都可作介词，表示“在附近”，但也有细微差别。<br />
<strong>by</strong> 表示距离较近，含“在旁边”之意。
<strong>near</strong> 有时表示距离较远。</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We live near the sea.
我们住得离海很近。(通常看不到海)</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>在…之前；在…期间：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>by day / night
在白天/夜间</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>By this time tomorrow, I’ll be there.
明天这个时候，我会到那儿。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>By the end of last year, my vocabulary had grown to 3,000 words. 
到去年末，我的词汇量已达到了3000。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>被；由：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The play was written by Shakespeare. 
此剧为莎士比亚所著。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Washing hands often is one of the effective ways to avoid being infected by diseases. 
勤洗手是避免疾病传染的有效方法之一。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.★ <strong>用；凭借；通过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>by bus / boat / air
乘公共汽车/船/飞机</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He saluted us by raising his hat.
他举帽向我们敬礼。</p></div>

<h4 id="5">5.★ <strong>抓着 (物体或身体的某个部位)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I caught him by the arm.
我抓住了他的胳膊。</p></div>

<h4 id="6">6.★ <strong>由于：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We met by chance at the airport.
我们在机场不期而遇。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ve taken someone else’s bag by mistake.
我误拿了别人的包。</p></div>

<h4 id="7">7.★ <strong>经由；经过：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I’ll go to Japan by Canada.
我将经加拿大去日本。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He walked by me without noticing me.
他从我身旁走过，没注意到我。</p></div>

<h4 id="8">8.★ <strong>相差：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>increase by 30%
增长30%</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>miss the train by 10 minutes
差10分钟没赶上火车</p></div>

<h4 id="9">9.★ <strong>根据；按：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are paid by the hour.
我们按小时计酬。</p></div>

<h4 id="10">10.★ <strong>长…宽；用…乘 / 除：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The box is 40 cm by 60 cm.
这个盒子40厘米宽，60厘米长。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>multiply 10 by 2
10乘以2</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>divide 20 by 5
20除以5</p></div>

<h4 id="11">11.★ <strong>：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>day by day / one by one / step by step
一天天/一个接一个/一步步</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>I showed them I was independent by wear strange clothes.  （2016 全国 改错）  </li>
<li>Nowadays some hospitals refer to patients <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ name, not case number.  （2010 江西改）  </li>
<li>If you really have to leave during the meeting, you’d better leave <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the back door.  （2008 北京）<br />
A.for<br />
B.by<br />
C.across<br />
D.out  </li>
<li>A great man shows his greatness <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ the way he treats little men.  （2008 福建改）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. wear → wearing  2. by  3. B  4. by  </p></div>